TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT DISTINCT TR.RPT_ID, TM.CORP_CD, TR.HRCY_RLTV_PSTN_VL, TR.RPT_TYP_CD, TR.START_DT, TR.END_DT, TR.RT_BASIS_TYP_CD, TR.RPT_TITLE, TR.DOT_OPERATION_CD, TR.MKSR_AGGR_LVL_CD, TR.NUM_LOG_CD, TR.FLOW_THRU_CD RPT_FLW_THRU_CD, TR.ADMN_EXCL_GRP_ID RPT_ADM_FE_EXGP_ID, TR.INEX_LINK_RPT_ID, TR.SEG_CD, TR.CREATE_USER_ID, TR.CREATE_TS, TR.UPDT_USER_ID, TR.UPDT_TS, TR.ADMN_FEE_FUND_CD, TR.NO_DATA_OUTP_CD, TR.HRCY_ID, ADM.DRUG_PRC_TERM_CD RPT_ADM_DP_TRM_CD, ADM.DRUG_PRC_TYP_CD RPT_ADM_DP_TYP_CD, BAS.DRUG_PRC_TERM_CD RPT_BAS_DP_TRM_CD, BAS.DRUG_PRC_TYP_CD RPT_BAS_DP_TYP_CD, CNT.DRUG_PRC_TERM_CD RPT_CNT_DP_TRM_CD, CNT.DRUG_PRC_TYP_CD RPT_CNT_DP_TYP_CD, FRM.DRUG_PRC_TERM_CD RPT_FRM_DP_TRM_CD, FRM.DRUG_PRC_TYP_CD RPT_FRM_DP_TYP_CD, PRF.DRUG_PRC_TERM_CD RPT_PRF_DP_TRM_CD, PRF.DRUG_PRC_TYP_CD RPT_PRF_DP_TYP_CD, PRP.DRUG_PRC_TERM_CD RPT_PRP_DP_TRM_CD, PRP.DRUG_PRC_TYP_CD RPT_PRP_DP_TYP_CD, --Added as part of ITPR006540 Price Protection (12/04/2014) ADM.DRUG_PRC_GRP_CD AS RPT_ADM_DP_GRP_CD, BAS.DRUG_PRC_GRP_CD AS RPT_BAS_DP_GRP_CD, CNT.DRUG_PRC_GRP_CD AS RPT_CNT_DP_GRP_CD, FRM.DRUG_PRC_GRP_CD AS RPT_FRM_DP_GRP_CD, PRF.DRUG_PRC_GRP_CD AS RPT_PRF_DP_GRP_CD, PRP.DRUG_PRC_GRP_CD AS RPT_PRP_DP_GRP_CD
FROM VRAP.TRPT_REQMT TR INNER JOIN VRAP.VREPORT R ON TR.RPT_ID = R.RPT_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.THIERARCHY TH ON R.HRCY_ID=TH.HRCY_ID LEFT JOIN VRAP.TRPT_REQMT_REV_TYP ADM ON R.RPT_ID=ADM.RPT_ID AND ADM.REV_TYP_CD=1 LEFT JOIN VRAP.TRPT_REQMT_REV_TYP BAS ON R.RPT_ID=BAS.RPT_ID AND BAS.REV_TYP_CD=2 LEFT JOIN VRAP.TRPT_REQMT_REV_TYP CNT ON R.RPT_ID=CNT.RPT_ID AND CNT.REV_TYP_CD=4 LEFT JOIN VRAP.TRPT_REQMT_REV_TYP FRM ON R.RPT_ID=FRM.RPT_ID AND FRM.REV_TYP_CD=3 LEFT JOIN VRAP.TRPT_REQMT_REV_TYP PRF ON R.RPT_ID=PRF.RPT_ID AND PRF.REV_TYP_CD=5 INNER JOIN VRAP.TCORP_MODEL_TYP_CD TM ON R.MODEL_TYP_CD = TM.MODEL_TYP_CD LEFT JOIN VRAP.TRPT_REQMT_REV_TYP PRP ON R.RPT_ID=PRP.RPT_ID AND PRP.REV_TYP_CD=6 WHERE (TR.UPDT_TS>TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS') OR TR.RPT_ID IN (SELECT UTS.RPT_ID FROM VRAP.TRPT_REQMT_REV_TYP UTS WHERE UTS.UPDT_TS>TIMESTAMP('$$LOAD_LAST_TS'))) WITH UR

) ,1,0)
